### Weather API Tests

# Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### Test hello endpoint
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/hello

###
### Full Weather Data Endpoint
###

### Get weather for auto-detected location (based on IP)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/weather

### Get weather for Paris
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/weather?location=Paris

### Get weather for New York
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/weather?location=New York

###
### Simple Rain Check Endpoint (only returns will_rain_today boolean)
### Automatically detects your city from IP if no location is provided
###

### Will it rain today? (auto-detected location from IP)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/will-it-rain

### Will it rain in Paris today?
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/will-it-rain?location=Paris

### Will it rain in New York today?
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/will-it-rain?location=New York

### Will it rain in Tokyo today?
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/will-it-rain?location=Tokyo

### Will it rain in London today?
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/will-it-rain?location=London

